.alert.alert-warning
  Please reload the page after inserting or updating a Flickr widget to display all changes.

%h4
  Display

= cms_edit_enum(widget, :display)

%h4
  Count

= cms_edit_enum(widget, :count, data: { editor: 'slider' })

%h4
  Size

= cms_edit_enum(widget, :size)

%h4
  Source

= cms_edit_enum(widget, :source)

%h4
  User

%p.text-info
  Please provide a user ID. Figure out the <a href="http://idgettr.com/">Flickr user ID</a> based on
  a username. The ID is only relevant if you select <strong>user</strong> or
  <strong>user_tag</strong> as a source.

= cms_tag(:div, widget, :user)

%h4
  Tags

%p.text-info
  Tags are a comma-separated list and only relevant if you select <strong>all_tag</strong> or
  <strong>user_tag</strong> as a source.

= cms_tag(:div, widget, :tags)
